make it so that it's very easy

00:34:12.600 --> 00:34:16.020
to take different types of
physical devices like this,

00:34:16.020 --> 00:34:19.139
and with different sensors--
accelerometers, light sensors,

00:34:19.139 --> 00:34:21.227
whatever, you know,
buttons, knobs--

00:34:21.227 --> 00:34:22.810
and be able to
wirelessly communicate.

