These are all Bluetooth
communication.

00:34:26.699 --> 00:34:28.770
In addition to extending
it through hardware,

00:34:28.770 --> 00:34:31.760
we're going to extend
things either to a web based

00:34:31.760 --> 00:34:34.547
or software side.

00:34:34.547 --> 00:34:36.380
Here's an example that's
already in Scratch,

00:34:36.380 --> 00:34:38.990
because of the spirit of the
